comment: Jackson and Reilly paper has typographical error in value for a(12). - _Sean A. Irvine_, Jun 17 2015
reference: N. J. A. Sloane and Simon Plouffe, The Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences, Academic Press, 1995 (includes this sequence).

D. M. Jackson and J. W. Reilly, The enumeration of homeomorphically irreducible labeled graphs, J. Combin. Theory, B 19 (1975), 272-286.
formula: E.g.f.: log(B(x)) where B(x) is the e.g.f. for A003514. - _Sean A. Irvine_, Jun 17 2015
program: seq(n)={my(A=O(x*x^n)); Vec(serlaplace(log((exp(x/2 - x^2/4 + A)/sqrt(1 + x + A))*sum(k=0, n, (2*exp(-x/(1+x) + A))^binomial(k,2) * (x*exp((x^2 + A)/(2*(1 + x))))^k / k!))), -(n+1))} \\ _Andrew Howroyd_, Jan 24 2020
